       DETAIL
*      LJUST(W) LEFT JUSTIFIES A BCD WORD 
*      KEEPS LEADING ZEROS. SET TRAILING BLANKS 
*      RETURNS '*' IF WORD IS ALL BLANKS  
       REM
       LBL     LJUST
       ENTRY   LJUST
       REM
LJUST  SYN     *  
X4     SYN     *-2
       SXD     X4,4     
       CAL*    1,4
       STI     B  
       LDQ     =H     * 
       AXT     6,4
A      PAI  
       IIL     600000   
       LFT     770000   
       TRA     D  
       LGL     6  
       TIX     A,4,1    
D      XCL  
       XCA  
       LDI     B  
       LXD     X4,4     
       TRA     2,4
B     
       END  
